                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/11/176148810/fecf89a6a9b22c356816fea1c2cae7f3_7732712191092989867.png",
                      "menu_id": 17,
                      "name": "Kamisato Ayato",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "ได้รับชัยชนะภายใน 6 เทิร์น",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3712,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/11/176148810/aa97e1efe8785d33bb6ea0912cb42e94_1533895118746516039.png",
                      "menu_id": 18,
                      "name": "Kyouka Fuushi",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "ชนะโดยจำนวนตัวละครที่ถูกกำจัดต่ำกว่า 2 ตัว",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3712,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/11/176148810/aa97e1efe8785d33bb6ea0912cb42e94_1533895118746516039.png",
                      "menu_id": 18,
                      "name": "Kyouka Fuushi",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "การต่อสู้อย่างจริงจัง",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "แนะนำด่าน",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "\"หากเป็นการดูเอลกับคุณ เช่นนั้นก็น่าจะเต็มไปด้วยความรื่นรมย์ล่ะนะ... ก็ดี งั้นมาสนุกกันสักตาเถอะ\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(236, 229, 216)"
                      ],
                      "text": "[กฎพิเศษ] ในตอนเริ่ม \"Kamisato Ayato\" จะติดตั้งการ์ดพรสวรรค์ \"Kyouka Fuushi\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "ทีมของคู่ต่อสู้",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3708,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/11/176148810/fecf89a6a9b22c356816fea1c2cae7f3_7732712191092989867.png",
                      "menu_id": 17,
                      "name": "Kamisato Ayato",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
